      "expected": "Tab B should revalidate or clearly refresh cached store list after another tab mutates store data, especially after route return/history navigation.",
      "actual": "Tab B kept showing the old store name until hard refresh/manual refresh.",
      "refreshRecovers": true,
      "networkObservation": "No automatic /api/stores revalidation was observed in the stale tab during route return/history checks."
    },
